==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Below one person, above 10,000 people.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī rén zhī xià, wàn rén zhī shàng

===Idiom===
'''[[一人之下，萬人之上]]'''

# To occupy a lofty position, second only to the emperor.

===Alternate forms===
[[一人之下，万人之上]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

